            "t": "text",
            "v": "Let this day be an offering of abstinence in purity to The Lord, a giving of thanks for your sins atoned for by The Messiah YahuShua; not atonement for your sins, of yourselves, but a free will offering in the name of The Lord your God and Him crucified, rejoicing in the anticipation of The Blessed Hope. And behold, He shall sit upon the throne of His glory and judge the nations. He shall utterly destroy all wickedness from this world, wiping away all that is sin and that which has led His people astray."
